委内瑞拉政府认为，抗议者是想要重复{{link-en|2002年委内瑞拉政变企图|2002 Venezuelan coup d'état attempt}}。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://rt.com/news/venezuela-riots-kill-students-827/ |title=Venezuela coup? Gunfire, clashes as 3 dead in violent Caracas protest (PHOTOS, VIDEO) — RT News |publisher=Rt.com |date=12 February 2014 |accessdate=16 February 2014 |archive-date=2014-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140305113815/http://rt.com/news/venezuela-riots-kill-students-827/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>委内瑞拉政府称，美国政府正在积极支持反对派，并指控其插手委内瑞拉的事务，并试图通过其“软政变”的战术动摇马杜罗总统政府。<ref>[http://www.telesurtv.net/articulos/2014/02/20/el-golpe-suave-en-venezuela-en-cinco-pasos-7713.html "El 'golpe suave' en Venezuela en cinco pasos"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.telesurtv.net/articulos/2014/02/20/el-golpe-suave-en-venezuela-en-cinco-pasos-7713.html |date=20140302074300 }}. [[TeleSUR|TeleSUR]]. 20 February 2014.</ref>[[尼古拉斯·马杜罗|尼古拉斯·马杜罗]]总统曾说过：“从2月12日开始，我们已经进入了一个极右的新的时期，（这时期）无法赢得民主，而是赢得了恐惧、暴力、诡计和操纵媒体。他们因为美国政府的支持而倍具信心，尽管他们的行为愈加暴力。”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://afgj.org/alliance-for-global-justice-statement-on-right-wing-violence-in-venezuela |title=Alliance for Global Justice Statement on Right-Wing Violence in Venezuela | Alliance for Global Justice |publisher=Afgj.org |date= |accessdate=21 February 2014 |archive-date=2014-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222022601/http://afgj.org/alliance-for-global-justice-statement-on-right-wing-violence-in-venezuela |dead-url=no }}</ref>马杜罗还称，[[巴拿马|巴拿马]]政府也在过多干预委内瑞拉政府。<ref>{{cite news|title=Venezuela acusa a Panamá de injerencia y llama a consultas a su embajadora|url=http://www.lapatilla.com/site/2014/02/20/maduro-llamo-a-consulta-a-embajadora-venezolana-en-panama/|accessdate=20 February 2014|newspaper=La Patilla|date=20 February 2014|archive-date=2014-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140225001156/http://www.lapatilla.com/site/2014/02/20/maduro-llamo-a-consulta-a-embajadora-venezolana-en-panama/|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[美国|美国]]的行政部门已否认所有参与委内瑞拉政治事务的指控并要求抗议者和委内瑞拉政府官员之间进行和平对话。<ref>{{cite news|title=White House: US not backing Venezuela opposition protests|url=http://america.aljazeera.com/articles/2014/2/17/venezuela-expels3usdiplomatsamidprotestviolence.html|accessdate=18 February 2014|newspaper=Al Jazeera|date=18 February 2014|archive-date=2014-02-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140218020102/http://america.aljazeera.com/articles/2014/2/17/venezuela-expels3usdiplomatsamidprotestviolence.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

安全部队对示威者和记者做出了不少人权侵犯行为。<ref>{{cite web|title=Venezuela: Violence Against Protesters, Journalists|url=http://www.hrw.org/news/2014/02/21/venezuela-violence-against-protesters-journalists|publisher=Human Rights Watch|accessdate=23 February 2014|archive-date=2015-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150313043202/http://www.hrw.org/news/2014/02/21/venezuela-violence-against-protesters-journalists|dead-url=no}}</ref>马杜罗总统先是组织亲政府的示威活动，并宣布禁止暴力反政府抗议活动。<ref name="permiso">[http://www.infobae.com/2014/02/13/1543394-violencia-venezuela-maduro-anuncio-que-los-que-se-movilicen-sin-permiso-seran-detenidos Violencia en Venezuela: Maduro anunció que los que se movilicen "sin permiso" serán detenidos] {{Wayback|url=http://www.infobae.com/2014/02/13/1543394-violencia-venezuela-maduro-anuncio-que-los-que-se-movilicen-sin-permiso-seran-detenidos |date=20140302230023 }}. Infobae</ref>被称为“colectivos”的武装组织被指控攻击反对派电视台的工作人员，并给记者发送死亡威胁，并在[[乌戈·查韦斯|乌戈·查韦斯]]指责[[梵蒂冈|梵蒂冈]]特使干预政府后向其投掷[[催泪瓦斯|催泪瓦斯]]来协助政府。<ref>{{cite news|last=Wallis|first=Daniel|title=Venezuela violence puts focus on militant 'colectivo' groups|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/02/13/venezuela-protests-colectivos-idUSL2N0LI14W20140213|accessdate=22 February 2014|newspaper=Reuters|date=13 February 2014|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924193514/http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/02/13/venezuela-protests-colectivos-idUSL2N0LI14W20140213|dead-url=yes}}</ref>{{link-en|委内瑞拉全国民兵|Venezuelan National Militia|玻利瓦尔民兵组织}}是查韦斯政府培养，用于强化人民武装，防止反动势力进行武装颠覆的民兵组织，它有时也会“暴力压制异己或不听从于政府的记者”。<ref>{{cite news|last=Munera|first=Isabel|title=Los guardianes de la revolución|url=http://www.elmundo.es/internacional/2014/02/24/530ba27c268e3e5f388b4581.html|accessdate=25 February 2014|newspaper=El Mundo|date=24 February 2014|archive-date=2014-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140303132428/http://www.elmundo.es/internacional/2014/02/24/530ba27c268e3e5f388b4581.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>这一组织被定义为“拿着武器的平民” 或者是 “战斗的身躯”，由来自公共机构，大学和公司的成员们组成。<ref>{{cite web|author=中国网军事|title=委内瑞拉政府准备培养100万民兵 捍卫革命成果|url=http://military.china.com.cn/2013-10/25/content_30402222.htm|accessdate=2014-03-05|archive-date=2014-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140305164551/http://military.china.com.cn/2013-10/25/content_30402222.htm|dead-url=yes}}</ref>{{link-en|El国民队 (加拉加斯)|El Nacional (Caracas)|El国民队}}声称，这些人攻击反对派的目的是杀死他们，因为许多示威者直接被枪杀在不易察觉的地区。<ref>{{cite news|title=El objetivo de agresores ha sido matar a manifestantes|url=http://www.el-nacional.com/sucesos/objetivo-agresores-matar-manifestantes_0_361764049.html|accessdate=26 February 2014|newspaper=El Nacional|date=25 February 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140225213846/http://www.el-nacional.com/sucesos/objetivo-agresores-matar-manifestantes_0_361764049.html|archivedate=2014年2月25日}}</ref>

