[[泛美新闻协会|泛美新闻协会]]抗议当局采用阻断互联网、禁止频道、撤销外国媒体凭证、骚扰记者和限制印刷报纸资源等手段，“官方审查”媒体<ref>{{cite web|title=IAPA protests official censorship of press in Venezuela|url=http://www.sipiapa.org/en/iapa-protests-official-censorship-of-press-in-venezuela/|work=Press Release|publisher=Inter American Press Association|accessdate=26 February 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140302123447/http://www.sipiapa.org/en/iapa-protests-official-censorship-of-press-in-venezuela/|archivedate=2014年3月2日}}</ref>。委内瑞拉外国新闻记者协会同时谴责政府对记者实施殴打、虐待、骚乱、威胁和抢劫<ref name= AFNCattacks>{{cite news|title=La APEX demanda al Gobierno a que se respete a periodistas extranjeros|url=http://www.eluniversal.com/nacional-y-politica/protestas-en-venezuela/140222/la-apex-demanda-al-gobierno-a-que-se-respete-a-periodistas-extranjeros|accessdate=26 February 2014|newspaper=El Universal|date=25 February 2014|archive-date=2014-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140310060058/http://www.eluniversal.com/nacional-y-politica/protestas-en-venezuela/140222/la-apex-demanda-al-gobierno-a-que-se-respete-a-periodistas-extranjeros|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。委内瑞拉全国记者联盟曾表示，目前已有至少181名记者受到攻击，有82例骚乱、40例肢体侵犯、35例抢劫或销毁工作材料、23例逮捕和枪伤，“集体党”至少策划20起袭击<ref name= SNTPattacks>{{cite news|title=Sntp: 181 agresiones, robos y detenciones contra periodistas en dos meses de protesta|url=http://www.lapatilla.com/site/2014/04/12/sntp-181-agresiones-robos-y-detenciones-contra-periodistas-en-dos-meses-de-protesta/|accessdate=13 April 2014|newspaper=La Patilla|date=12 April 2014|archive-date=2014-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140417033940/http://www.lapatilla.com/site/2014/04/12/sntp-181-agresiones-robos-y-detenciones-contra-periodistas-en-dos-meses-de-protesta/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=SNTP registra más de 120 agresiones contra periodistas|url=http://www.eluniversal.com/nacional-y-politica/protestas-en-venezuela/140312/sntp-registra-mas-de-120-agresiones-contra-periodistas|accessdate=12 March 2014|newspaper=El Universal|date=12 March 2014|archive-date=2014-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141204150501/http://www.eluniversal.com/nacional-y-politica/protestas-en-venezuela/140312/sntp-registra-mas-de-120-agresiones-contra-periodistas|dead-url=no}}</ref>。为回应报纸短缺和13家委内瑞拉报社的关闭，哥伦比亚报纸组织Andiarios发起“我们都是委内瑞拉人，无新闻自由，无民主”运动，用大篷车将52吨资源运往向《国民报》、《搏动报》和《努埃沃国家报》，以协助保卫“新闻自由和知情权<ref>{{cite news|title=Diarios de Colombia les dan papel a periódicos venezolanos|url=http://www.eltiempo.com/mundo/latinoamerica/entrega-de-papel-para-periodicos-venezolanos_13760398-4|accessdate=1 April 2014|newspaper=El Tiempo|date=31 March 2014|archive-date=2014-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407081538/http://www.eltiempo.com/mundo/latinoamerica/entrega-de-papel-para-periodicos-venezolanos_13760398-4|dead-url=no}}</ref>”。波多黎各、巴拿马、特立尼达和多巴哥的报社，也将报纸运往委内瑞拉，协助缓解当局价格限制造成的报纸短缺<ref>{{cite news|title=Puerto Rico, Panamá y Trinidad también ofrecen papel a diarios venezolanos|url=http://www.lapatilla.com/site/2014/04/11/puerto-rico-panama-y-trinidad-tambien-ofrecen-papel-a-diarios-venezolanos/|accessdate=12 April 2014|newspaper=La Patilla|date=11 April 2014|archive-date=2014-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140413124406/http://www.lapatilla.com/site/2014/04/11/puerto-rico-panama-y-trinidad-tambien-ofrecen-papel-a-diarios-venezolanos/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

当局限制媒体报道，RCTV和Globovision等反政府电视台分别被吊销执照，被迫变动股权<ref name="socialmediakey">{{cite news|title=Social media key for Venezuelan protesters|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/world/2014/02/19/venezuela-uprising-protests/5606899/|author=Peter Wilson|newspaper=USA Today|date=19 February 2014|accessdate=2014-03-04|archive-date=2014-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140304210153/http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/world/2014/02/19/venezuela-uprising-protests/5606899/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。反对派表示，政府持有“电台、电视台和报纸的庞大结构，依靠公共资金建立通讯霸权，无需央行提供经济或是记者犯罪统计数据等可靠信息<ref>{{cite news|last=Vinogradoff|first=Ludmila|title=Maduro trata a la prensa aún peor que Hugo Chávez|url=http://www.abc.es/internacional/20140303/abcp-chavez-maduro-prensa-20140301.html#.UxUJhwu4zFs.twitter|accessdate=4 March 2014|newspaper=ABC (Spain)|date=3 March 2014|archive-date=2015-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150123232749/http://www.abc.es/internacional/20140303/abcp-chavez-maduro-prensa-20140301.html#.UxUJhwu4zFs.twitter|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

